# Jade

# jade 2 html
Given (command/jade/pipe1):
  a(href='#')
    h1 title

Execute (command/jade/pipe1):
  call transformer#cmd('Jade')
    \.src(S.buf('%'))
    \.exec(
    \   M.pipe('jade --pretty'),
    \   M.buf('%')
    \)
  Jade

Expect (command/exec/pipe1/result):
  <a href="#">
    <h1>title</h1></a>


